		// 1. Add ownerKey parameter to EntityClient.loadMultiple()
		// 2. Add ownerKey parameter to EntityRestClient.loadMultiple()
		// 3. Pass ownerKey through _handleLoadMultipleResult to _decryptMapAndMigrate
		// 4. Use ownerKey in _decryptMapAndMigrate to resolve session keys

